			<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.82fr_1.18fr] lg:items-start">
				<div>
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase text-eden-green">$299 Peptide Starter</p>
					<h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-eden-navy sm:text-4xl">
						Know where to start for $299.
