					<p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 text-slate-700">
						One clear first step: a private consultation with a licensed provider, baseline lab work, and a personalized next-step plan. No treatment purchase is included or required.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-6 rounded-lg border border-eden-line bg-eden-paper p-5 shadow-sm">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase text-eden-green">$299 — Peptide Starter</p>
						<ul class="mt-4 grid gap-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">
							{pricingIncludes.map((item) => (
								<li class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-eden-green"></span>
