							One peptide-first starting point before choosing a protocol.
						</h2>
					</div>
					<p class="text-base leading-8 text-slate-700">
						This visit is built for people actively comparing peptide therapy, peptide injections, peptide clinics, recovery, body composition, skin quality, and longevity-minded wellness support.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
					{lanes.map((item) => (
						<div class="rounded-lg border border-eden-line bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
							<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-eden-green">Care path</p>
							<h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-eden-navy">{item.label}</h3>
							<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">{item.body}</p>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="why-eden" class="bg-white px-6 py-12 sm:py-16">
