				<div>
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase text-eden-green">Clinical team</p>
					<h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-eden-navy sm:text-4xl">
						Reviewed by Eden's clinical team.
